## ⏱️ Complexity Analysis

Let `m` be the number of restrictions.

### Time Complexity

* Sorting restrictions: `O(m log m)`
* Left-to-right pass: `O(m)`
* Right-to-left pass: `O(m)`
* Peak computation: `O(m)`

Overall:

```text
O(m log m)
```

### Space Complexity

```text
O(m)
```

for storing the processed restrictions.

